      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "@Ava as of now, we can configure <code>ObjectMapper</code> to not fail for unknown propertie: <code>new ObjectMapper().configure(FAIL_ON_UNKNOWN_PROPERTIES, false);</code> Other configurable stuffs: <a href=\"https://fasterxml.github.io/jackson-databind/javadoc/2.6/com/fasterxml/jackson/databind/DeserializationFeature.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">fasterxml.github.io/jackson-databind/javadoc/2.6/com/fasterx&zwnj;&#8203;ml/&hellip;</a>"
