      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "I beg to differ but if the fields change name, this will silently fail and we have no idea what is happening unless we check field by field. In my case, it even <b>ignores the failure when the DTO lacks any field definition</b>, which is very dangerous. So it will ignore the failure no matter what type is; use with caution."
