      "body" : "Upvote.  But adding a link for &quot;with di.xml&quot;. (dependency injection .xm) : <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/14343477/how-do-you-globally-set-jackson-to-ignore-unknown-properties-within-spring/14343479#14343479\" title=\"how do you globally set jackson to ignore unknown properties within spring\">stackoverflow.com/questions/14343477/&hellip;</a>"
